00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:47,320
Whatever path you walk, I'll follow.

847
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,400
With you following me,

848
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,480
any path would lead

849
00:39:49,590 --> 00:39:50,460
straight to hell.

850
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:51,540
Wait, Song Yimeng.

851
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,230
I'll tell you one last time:

852
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,280
until I calm down,

853
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,620
don't let me see your face!

854
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:06,990
Song Yimeng!

855
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:09,250
When will you calm down?

856
00:40:10,550 --> 00:40:11,320
Song Yimeng!

857
00:40:18,710 --> 00:40:20,280
The Pingrong Battle

858
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,960
was a national tragedy.

859
00:40:22,160 --> 00:40:26,000
Gao Changyin and his accomplices

860
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:23,510
[Gao Residence]

861
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:27,670
conspired against their own country.

862
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:26,920
[Gao Residence]

863
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:30,880
Because of them,
20,000 Qianyu soldiers were slaughtered.

864
00:40:28,450 --> 00:40:31,800
[Sealed by the capital prefect Chu
following a royal command]

865
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:32,430
Their crimes are unforgivable.

866
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:33,710
Their property is confiscated,

867
00:40:33,710 --> 00:40:35,480
and they're exiled
to the northern frontier.

868
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,880
All titles and ranks

869
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,710
are stripped.

870
00:40:38,710 --> 00:40:40,510
Let this be a warning

871
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:42,590
to all officials.

872
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:46,500
Thank goodness
I sided with the Seventh Prince.

873
00:40:48,650 --> 00:40:55,920
[Yan Gate]

